{"lang": "en_US", "eventid": "act48side", "eventName": "Medjehtiqedti Bound", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "ME-4", "avgTag": "After Operation", "storyName": "Misstep", "storyInfo": "Xanthos steals the harp. Titi catches up to him by the riverbank, but the precious relic is accidentally dropped as they fight over it.\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "duration": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "69_g14_luxuriousroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$plot_intro", "key": "$plot_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "duration": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4166_varkis_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The room of the Sargonian ambassador... this is the relic that was stolen a century ago?", "name": "Xanthos"}, "figure_art": "avg_4166_varkis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4166_varkis_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The tall Minoan peers at the massive wooden box as he starts the motor on his serrated oar, repurposing the tool that he uses to cross the river to pick the lock open."}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "He carefully lifts the cover of the box. The instrument of Kereseira, which should have come home long ago, is safely packaged in a dust cover."}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4166_varkis_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Kereseira's harp must not be used as a bargaining chip by the Sargonian hypocrites, to be shut away in this pretentious, suffocating box...", "name": "Xanthos"}, "figure_art": "avg_4166_varkis_1#3$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4166_varkis_1#3$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Put the harp down, Xanthos.", "name": "Pallas"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_482_pallas_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4056_titi_1#1$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4166_varkis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The people praise you for proposing the rebuilding of the First Temple as soon as you returned to Athenius, Pallas. I voted in favor myself.", "name": "Xanthos"}, "figure_art": "avg_4166_varkis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_482_pallas_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4056_titi_1#1$2", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Thank you.", "name": "Pallas"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_482_pallas_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4166_varkis_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "But you should not have cozied up to the Sargonians.", "name": "Xanthos"}, "figure_art": "avg_4166_varkis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_482_pallas_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4056_titi_1#11$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "Titi"}, "figure_art": "avg_4056_titi_1#11$2"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "You instructed your apprentice to ram the hotel kitchen and cause a fire, letting you sneak in to steal an artifact of great diplomatic significance to our two countries... it's an ill-advised act.", "name": "Titi"}, "figure_art": "avg_4056_titi_1#11$2"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The streets outside the hotel are packed with people. You can't possibly escape with the harp.", "name": "Titi"}, "figure_art": "avg_4056_titi_1#11$2"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4166_varkis_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "Xanthos"}, "figure_art": "avg_4166_varkis_1#14$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "delay", "attribu