: "avg_4056_titi_1#10$2"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avgnew_482_pallas_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Wisdom.", "name": "Pallas"}, "figure_art": "avgnew_482_pallas_1#7$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "69_g5_athenusalley", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2070_1#6$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2088_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The fire is under control, Grammateús. As for the hotel's losses...", "name": "Peace Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2088_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2070_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "I'll report the incident to the Astynomos' Office per official procedures. As for the damage to the kitchen, I've already settled up with the innkeeper.", "name": "Hekádemos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2070_1#6$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2088_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "I see. We'll station someone here to make sure no one's trying to take advantage of the chaos, for instance...", "name": "Peace Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2088_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2070_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "What is it?", "name": "Hekádemos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2070_1#6$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2088_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "L-Look up!", "name": "Peace Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2088_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_windowbreak", "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_doorbreak", "channel": "3"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Hekádemos looks up."}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "A pair of Forte horns, pitch-black under the sunlight like the twin moons, flies over the head of the crowd, their owner landing upon a haystack on the accident boat, before leaping off the boat and fleeing along the river."}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "false", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "A few seconds later, a white figure leaps from the window off the end of a silver chain. The black Feline's landing is softened by several cloth ribbons surrounding her."}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2088_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Xanthos the ferryman? And the Sargonian ambassador?", "name": "Peace Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2088_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "What's that huge thing Xanthos is carrying on his back...? Don't tell me...", "name": "Peace Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2088_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2070_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "Hekádemos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2070_1#9$1"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "You were right, officer. Someone IS trying to take advantage of the chaos.", "name": "Hekádemos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2070_1#9$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2088_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Understood. Cordon the scene and impound that boat! Send someone to follow Kyría Mashayer and bring Xanthos into custody!", "name": "Peace Officer"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2088_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "69_g5_athenusalley", "screenadapt": "cove